thothbot.parallax.core.shared.core

Class Vector3

  • java.lang.Object
    • thothbot.parallax.core.shared.core.Vector2
      • thothbot.parallax.core.shared.core.Vector3
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Vector
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Vector4

    public class Vector3
extends Vector2
implements Vector
    This class is realization of (X, Y, Z) vector. Where: X - x coordinate of the vector. Y - y coordinate of the vector. Z - z coordinate of the vector.
    Author:
    thothbot
